OL,5,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,6,     FThere's an emergency in East
OL,7,     FLondon when a 25-ton truck hits a
OL,8,     Frailway bridge. And Buzz needs to
OL,9,     Fco-ordinate a multi-agency
OL,10,     Ftaskforce when a refrigerated
OL,11,     Florry catches fire on the A42.
OL,12,G0300 Trucking Hell
OL,13,     FJobs include a bulker trailer
OL,14,     Fthat's burst into flames, a
OL,15,     Fheavily laden DAF truck that's
OL,16,     Fwedged in soft mud by a busy dual
OL,17,     Fcarriageway, and a tractor unit
OL,18,     Fwith a broken prop shaft.
